# =============================================================================
# TIA-P25 Standards Repository — .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Original TIA documents are copyrighted. Only derived/transformative works
# (summaries, implementation specs, opcode tables, context docs) are committed.
# The download script lets anyone fetch the originals from TIA's public library.
# =============================================================================

# ---- Copyrighted originals: never commit ----
*.pdf
*.zip
*.wav
*.pcm
*.dat

# ---- Full-text extractions: near-verbatim reproductions ----
*_Full_Text.md
*_full_text.md

# ---- Download script data files (large, regenerable) ----
tia_library_raw.json
tia_library_parsed.json
tia_library_entries.txt
_download_tia.log

# ---- Working/temp files ----
*.tmp
*.swp
*~

# ---- OS junk ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
